## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the scope of sources consulted. While the findings provide a broad overview, they may not capture all nuances of the gender pay gap across different regions and industries. Additionally, the complexity of factors contributing to the pay gap means that some elements may be underrepresented in this summary. Further research is needed to explore specific industry trends and the impact of policy changes on the gender pay gap.